<br>
<br>
If a guild kills Naggy, then yes they should get first claim to camp Ragefire, for however long it takes for Ragefire to spawn.  However, if they leave then the camp goes to whoever else it there.  <br>
<br>
When we camp Ragefire we try to keep a full group there the whole time, so that we can kill the Fire Giants as the spawn.  Possibly waiting for a few more people to help is all.<br>
<br>
Yes, it is a long, boring, difficult camp.  However, it is also THE most powerful, useful epic weapon.  Which most people agree is worth the camp.  <br>
<br>
